    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/20534\">#20534</a> generalizes all generalizable results (without changing statements) about Noetherian and Artinian. Partially enabled by the generalization of linear independence; the PR also generalizes two lemmas missed by <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/20480\">#20480</a>.</p>",
