    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah you don't get isomorphism with direct sum assuming only iSupIndep/irredundancy, though if working with rings/groups we have <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=linearIndepOn_iff_notMem_span#doc\">docs#linearIndepOn_iff_notMem_span</a> showing the equivalence.</p>",
